short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sync Codility submissions to your Github

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Effortlessly synchronize and organize your Codility tasks with your GitHub repository.

This extension will upload your Codility task, code submission, and score to your designated Github repository.

***

Free.
Open source with public license (MIT)
For users by users.
